OL,3,CHinckley mum says scrapping two-child
OL,4,Cbenefit cap will 'change her life'
OL,6,FA Hinckley mum of three says that
OL,7,Fscrapping the two child benefit cap
OL,8,Fwould "change her life" as she would
OL,9,Fbe able to afford to feed her family
OL,10,Fwithout having to use a foodbank.
OL,12,FIvy, who has chosen not to disclose
OL,13,Fher full name, is a regular user of a
OL,14,Ffoodbank in Hinckley which she says
OL,15,Fallows her to feed her children and
OL,16,Fher partner.
OL,18,FHinckley Area Foodbank helps families
OL,19,Fstock their cupboards with three days
OL,20,Fworth of basics.
