OL,6,FLast year, across their 9 sites in
OL,7,FHinckley and the surrounding area -
OL,8,Fthey fed over 6 thousand people - 2
OL,9,Fthousand of which were children.
OL,10,F(6,307 individual - 2,151 children)
OL,12,FThey say they're seeing more families
OL,13,Fthan ever pushed into hardship.
OL,15,FChild poverty is one of the key issues
OL,16,Fof the budget with campaigners saying
OL,17,Fscrapping the cap will lift as many as
OL,18,F350,000 children out of poverty.
