OL,3,CHinckley mum says scrapping two-child
OL,4,Cbenefit cap will 'change her life'
OL,6,FAccording to the End Child poverty
OL,7,Fcampaign, in the West Midlands, 36% of
OL,8,Fall children live in poverty which is
OL,9,Fthe highest rate in the country and in
OL,10,Fthe East Midlands, it's almost 30%
OL,11,Fwith some extreme pockets of
OL,12,Fdeprivation in major cities like
OL,13,FNottingham and Leicester where almost
OL,14,Fhalf a children live in poverty.
OL,16,FWhat is the two child benefit cap?
OL,18,FThe two child limit means that many
OL,19,Flow income families do not receive
OL,20,Ffurther benefits when they have a
OL,21,Fthird or subsequent child.
