OL,3,CHinckley mum says scrapping two-child
OL,4,Cbenefit cap will 'change her life'
OL,6,FPat Hancock, Project Manager at
OL,7,FHinckley Area foodbank says, "Parents
OL,8,Fwill be able to provide for families
OL,9,Fthemselves, we will always be here to
OL,10,Fsupport, this lifting won't stop
OL,11,Feverything but it will exit a lot of
OL,12,Fpeople that are just scraping through.
OL,14,F"It would be amazing and it would be
OL,15,Fthe answer to a lot of prayers, it
OL,16,Fwould bridge the gap between people
OL,17,Fbeing able to provide for their
OL,18,Ffamilies and coming to a foodbank."
